  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 440333c5586acf44db3ff057db103969, type: 3}
  m_Name: Day 1 Government Message
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  personSpokenTo: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b2bdc4a268c1abc4386e1f154d6bd7e5, type: 2}
  lines:
  - Due to experience working as a border control agent, you have been appointed
    with remotely handling citizen evacuations.
  - You are to inspect citizens for known symptoms of the virus and determine whether
    to send them in for further screening.
  - "Border control agents\u2019 evacuation will be handled individually after all
    other citizens."
  - On your computer you may find an application that will be used for this remote
    border control task.
  - Please read all information present within it and begin your shift as soon as
    possible.
